    // 💥 Updating UI from background thread = crash
    self.label.text = formatCurrentTime()
}

// Additionally, if the observer references a deallocated object → EXC_BAD_ACCESS
```

---

### 3. Null/Invalid Date Parsing

Cached date formatters or stored date strings become invalid after a timezone shift.

```swift
